needed the syntax to handle the pointers.

I think the easiest way will be to do

Newtype .Column
String.s
Align.w
Column.w
end newtype


Then 

NewType .Heading
HeadingCount.w
Pad.w
Columns[9].Column
End Newtype

Then 

Deftype.Heading Heading1, Heading2, *CurrentHeading

*CurrentHeading = &Heading1
gosub common
*CurrentHeading = &Heading2
Gosub common
end

Common
For i = 0 to *CurrentHeading\HeadingCount
	ThisString$ = *CurrentHeading\Columns[i]\String
next
return

