> sure you can figure out what is going on. 

I figured out where i was going wrong last night. I had been using an ASL 
requester to get the screenmode and used the width in that for the width of the 
screen, pixel array and the temporary bitmap. Which was stupid, as the screen's 
bitmap was obviously opened at whatever size is convenient for the card. I used 
GetBitMapAttr to get the width of the screen's bitmap after opening it and then 
used that size for my pixel array and temporary bitmap.

All seems lovely now :)

Thanks.

