other program can even use the same colours that you have locked.

This should be used with caution, especially if you are going to lock
several pens.  It is really only meant to be used if your program is going
to be changing the colour of that pen after locking it.

For standard remapping, ObtainBestPenA is a better choice.

Here are a couple of routines for using it.


