sourced from a early A2000HD machine.  What machine is this being fixed to?  

Also, in HDToolBox there is the 'Change Drive Type', you can enter the
details about a drive, and in those options is a cycler with the label
'Drive Types:' you can toggled that between SCSI and XT.  For more info
you'd need the Amiga Hard Disk User Manual, which I don't find atm.

